Follow the installation instruction below to play, grab, export MODs in
grabber.exe under DJGPP


Installation
------------
1.  Compile Allegro to get the liballeg.a copied to the djgpp\lib directory
    (if you haven't done so).

2.  Compile JGMOD to get the libjgmod.a copied to the djgpp\lib direcotry.
    (if you haven't done so). 

3.  Copy all the contents of this directory (jgmod\plugins) to the
    directory of allegro\tools\plugins. If other library also have plugin
    files, copy it as well.

4   Delete plugins.h in directory allegro\obj\djgpp

5.  Recompile allegro (without deleting Allegro, of course).

6.  Now you can grab, play MODs in the grabber.exe. Enjoy.

